text: Helen Ann Davies (born 29 July 1966) is an international cricketer who made 25 One Day International appearances for South Africa national women's cricket team between 1997 and 2000. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Cricketers from Cape Town Category:South African women cricketers Category:South Africa women One Day International cricketers
